# Anti-Patterns (Never Use)

## Obsolete paths & tooling

| ‚ùå Never | ‚úÖ Use instead |
|----------|----------------|
| `frontend/` | `apps/web/` |
| `backend/Api/` | `apps/api/` |
| `budget.db` | `app.db` / migrations |
| Axios | `fetch` via `apps/web/src/api/base/client.ts` |
| `@effect/schema` package | `effect` `Schema` module |
| `EnsureCreated()` | `Database.MigrateAsync()` in `DbInitializer` |
| `FrontendUrl` config key | `WebOrigin` / `WebOrigins` |
| Swashbuckle-only (no OpenAPI map) | `MapOpenApi()` + Scalar in dev |
| `.github/copilot-instructions.md` | `.cursor/rules/` + skills |
| Open CRUD without auth | `[Authorize]` on `BaseController<T>` |

## Examples

```csharp
// ‚ùå BAD
await context.Database.EnsureCreatedAsync();

// ‚úÖ GOOD ‚Äî DbInitializer.cs
await context.Database.MigrateAsync();
```

```typescript
// ‚ùå BAD
import axios from 'axios'

// ‚úÖ GOOD
import { httpClient } from '@/api/base/client'
```

```csharp
// ‚ùå BAD ‚Äî unauthenticated entity controller
public class TaskController : BaseController<TaskItem> { } // missing [Authorize] on base

// ‚úÖ GOOD ‚Äî BaseController already has [Authorize]
